data.description: Opportunity Knocks near Fort Ogden for someone with the vision to make this place their Million-Dollar Country Estate.  This property needs your discerning eye to make this dream a reality.  With just under 11 acres for the property, this was a cattle farm with ample pastures.  Inside the ranch, you'll be revamping the kitchen and baths and replacing the appliances which will undoubtedly make this place, a palace.  The pool is functioning but it has a couple of leaks and the surface needs to be upgraded.  The Barn blew down in the Hurricane but the slab is still there and looks good, but verify.   The Kennels which are a whole other structure have seen better days, and may not be any good, but there is potential to make it a new barn or another little house.  The chain link fencing is down but not out.  The pastures were all fenced and may still be, but not able to verify such as the brush being too thick with vegetation.  The grass hasn't been mowed in a while, and there is a pile of debris that requires a dumpster which will be moved away soon.  Opportunity is Knocking, who's going to answer?  All room sizes are approximate and not warranted.  "Sold only an AS-IS Cash Sale".
